{"tid":1511554,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"印尼政府宣佈遷都","createTime":"2019-08-27T14:34:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T14:34:21.000Z","uid":23120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ef0c7e5614d04c546d8ae8c290a411ae78614da1","tid":1511554,"uid":23120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:34:21.000Z","msg":"印尼政府昨宣佈遷都計劃，預計10年內會將首都由雅加達（Jakarta）遷至位於婆羅洲東加里曼丹省兩縣境內，新首都暫時未有名稱。<br />\n<br />\n印尼首都雅加達一直因人口過多而引發不少社會問題，加上因過度抽取地下水而令城市不斷下沉，以及面對地震威脅，遷都一直都是印尼主要議題。另遷都亦有望能平衡各省發展，減輕爪哇島負擔。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}